---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — StrataReport AI"
  description="How StrataReport AI collects, uses, and protects your data, including the data you upload to generate strata reports."
>
  <article class="prose">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>
      This Privacy Policy explains how StrataReport AI ("we", "us") collects, uses, and protects
      information when you use our services.
    </p>

    <h2>Information we collect</h2>
    <p>
      We collect account information you provide (name, email, organisation), data you upload to
      generate reports (rent rolls, ledgers, work orders, meeting minutes), and usage telemetry
      that helps us improve the product.
    </p>

    <h2>How we use information</h2>
    <p>
      We use uploaded data solely to generate reports for you and your organisation. We do not
      sell your data and we do not use your uploaded data to train third-party AI models without
      your explicit consent.
    </p>

    <h2>Data storage and security</h2>
    <p>
      Data is stored in Australia in encrypted form. Access is restricted to authorised personnel
      and is logged.
    </p>

    <h2>Your rights</h2>
    <p>
      You can request a copy of your data, ask us to correct or delete it, or close your account
      at any time by contacting <a href="mailto:privacy@stratareport.ai">privacy@stratareport.ai</a>.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      Questions about this policy? Email
      <a href="mailto:privacy@stratareport.ai">privacy@stratareport.ai</a>.
    </p>
  </article>
</Layout>
